  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "PLASTERER",
  "description": "<h1>Job Description & Requirements</h1><p>We are looking for an experienced <strong>Plasterer </strong>to join our construction and renovation team. The successful candidate will be responsible for surface preparation, plastering works, and finishing of walls and ceilings for residential and commercial projects across Singapore.<br /></p><h2>Roles & Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Prepare surfaces by cleaning, smoothing, and applying bonding agents</p></li><li><p>Apply plaster to walls, ceilings, partitions, and façades</p></li><li><p>Mix plaster materials to the correct consistency</p></li><li><p>Install plasterboard and cornices where required</p></li><li><p>Repair cracks, damaged plaster, and uneven surfaces</p></li><li><p>Ensure smooth and high-quality finishing</p></li><li><p>Follow site safety rules and company work procedures</p></li><li><p>Work with supervisors and team members to meet project timelines</p></li><li><p>Maintain tools and keep work areas clean and safe</p></li></ul><h2>Requirements</h2><ul><li><p>Ability to read basic construction drawings and instructions</p></li><li><p>Physically fit and able to work on site</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of workplace safety practices</p></li><li><p>Willing to work overtime, weekends, and at different job locations when required</p></li><li><p>Team player with good work attitude and reliability</p></li></ul><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p>",
